{
  "page": "Did you know/98",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>... that Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Patrek_of_King%27s_Mountain\" title=\"Patrek of King&#39;s Mountain\">Patrek of King's Mountain</a> is a reference to Patrick St. Denis, who runs a fantasy website called Pat's Fantasy Hotlist, and was included because <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> lost a bet to Patrick? Patrick is a fan of the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dallas_Cowboys\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Dallas Cowboys\">Dallas Cowboys</a>, while Martin is a fan of the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_York_Giants\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:New York Giants\">New York Giants</a>. The bet was that, if Martin lost, he would have to kill Patrick horribly in the book.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Ser Patrek's coat of arms is described as looking somewhat like the logo of the Dallas Cowboy,. and Patrek is eventually killed by <a href=\"/index.php/Wun_Wun\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wun Wun\">Wun Wun</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Giant\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Giant\">giant</a>, in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Did_you_know/98&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.npr.org/2012/09/15/161142894/thrones-author-george-r-r-martin-plays-not-my-job\">'Thrones' Author George R.R. Martin Plays Not My Job (September 14, 2013)</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404182112\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.005 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.006 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 33/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 190/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 114/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 3/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 496/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    1.213      1 Template:References\n100.00%    1.213      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:23601-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404182112 and revision id 217694\n -->\n",
